Apple hires Bruce Sewell as new General Counsel
 Apple announced yesterday that current Senior VP and General Counsel Daniel Cooperman is retiring at the end of September and that he will be replaced by Bruce Sewell.D. Bruce Sewell (the "D" standards for Durward) becomes the fourth
