Insider Activity


Individual




D. Bruce Sewell



Mr. D. Bruce Sewell is Independent Director at Vail Resorts, Inc. and Secretary, SVP-Legal & Government Affairs at Apple, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Vail Resorts, Inc.
Mr. Sewell was previously employed as Senior Vice President & General Counsel by Intel Corp., a Member by The District of Columbia Bar, a Member by California State Bar Association, and Partner by Brown & Bain P.A.
He received his undergraduate degree from Lancaster University and a graduate degree from George Washington University.



